270
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:02,334
Did I tell you that?

271
00:25:02,418 --> 00:25:06,254
Well, JJ, he thinks it's a once-in-a-lifetime
opportunity, but I don't see it that way, Kelly.

272
00:25:06,339 --> 00:25:08,256
I think that we got a lot of things that...

273
00:25:08,341 --> 00:25:10,676
Kell? Hey!

274
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,971
Do you remember when we were like that?

275
00:25:17,809 --> 00:25:19,267
Did you hear anything I said?

276
00:25:20,228 --> 00:25:22,688
I think I weighed
