287
00:26:05,356 --> 00:26:07,357
and we'd be miserable.

288
00:26:08,359 --> 00:26:11,611
Kelly, you belong on stage,
singing in front of thousands of people.

289
00:26:12,822 --> 00:26:14,781
You're probably right.

290
00:26:15,074 --> 00:26:16,908
I know I'm right.

291
00:26:26,586 --> 00:26:27,669
Up or down?

292
00:26:27,754 --> 00:26:31,840
I want it down and full. Like really...
Do you remember how it was in Little Rock?

293
00:26:32,216 --> 00:26:34,885
- How could I forget?
- Well, goddamn.

294
00:26:35,219 --> 00:26:36,428
Hey.

295
00:26:37,096 --> 00:26:38,180
You like?

296
00:26:38,431 --> 00:26:40,640
