338
00:29:11,584 --> 00:29:13,043
Thank you.

339
00:29:16,505 --> 00:29:20,050
Oh, my gosh. That's from Emmylou.
That is so nice.

340
00:29:20,718 --> 00:29:22,802
Hey. Did you find him?

341
00:29:22,887 --> 00:29:24,721
Yeah, he's dealing
with a wardrobe emergency.

342
00:29:24,805 --> 00:29:26,097
He said he'll be in when he's done.

343
00:29:27,475 --> 00:29:29,267
He had a wardrobe emergency?

344
00:29:42,990 --> 00:29:44,908
It's an exciting night tonight.

345
00:29:44,992 --> 00:29:49,454
Y'all are the first to hear one of the best
country lineups in the state of Texas.

346
00:29:49,538 --> 00:29:53,291
And to kick it off, we have a newcomer,
Mr Beau Hutton.

347
00:29:58,214 --> 00:30:02,300
Thank you.

348
00:30:04,178 --> 00:30:07,055
Short and sweet
